<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.5.11">
<l>kūṟutaloṉ ṟārā kuṭakkūtta vammāṉaik</l>
<l>kūṟutalē mēvik kurukūrc caṭakōpaṉ</l>
<l>kūṟiṉa vantātiyō rāyirattu ḷippattuṅ</l>
<l>kūṟutalval lāruḷarēl kūṭuvarvai kuntamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If there are those capable to recite</l>
<l>these ten in one thousand of Antāti that was recited</l>
<l>by Caṭakōpaṉ from Kurukūr, being attached to talking</l>
<l>about the lord who danced with pots whose [description] does not become full by any talk,</l>
	<l>they will join Vaikunta.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
